iowarp-core provides CMake targets:

Core Components:
    find_package(iowarp-core CONFIG REQUIRED)

    # Link to ChiMod libraries
    target_link_libraries(main PRIVATE
        chimaera::admin_client      # Admin ChiMod
        chimaera::bdev_client       # Block device ChiMod
        wrp_cte::core_client        # Context Transfer Engine (if enabled)
        wrp_cae::core_client        # Context Assimilation Engine (if enabled)
    )

Individual Components (advanced usage):
    find_package(HermesShm CONFIG REQUIRED)
    find_package(chimaera CONFIG REQUIRED)
    find_package(chimaera_admin CONFIG REQUIRED)
    find_package(chimaera_bdev CONFIG REQUIRED)
    find_package(wrp_cte_core CONFIG REQUIRED)
    find_package(wrp_cae_core CONFIG REQUIRED)

For more information, see:
    https://www.iowarp.ai/docs
